          <h2 class="block-title">Practice Privacy</h2>
    
    <div class="block-content">
      <div class="block-content-inner">
        <ul>
<li>
		<a href="https://pressfreedomfoundation.org/encryption-works">Encryption Works: How to Protect Your Privacy in the Age of NSA Surveillance</a>&nbsp;(Freedom of the Press Foundation)</li>
