		<a href="http://www.slashgeek.net/2012/06/15/how-to-be-completely-anonymous-online/">How To Be Completely Anonymous Online</a>&nbsp;(Slashgeek)</li>
<li>
		<a href="http://www.forbes.com/sites/kashmirhill/2012/08/23/10-incredibly-simple-things-you-should-be-doing-to-protect-your-privacy/">10 Incredibly Simple Things You Should Be Doing To Protect Your Privacy</a>&nbsp;(Forbes)</li>
</ul>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div> <!-- /block -->
			</div>
		<div style="clear:both"></div>
</div> <!-- end wrapper -->

